View Your Intelligent App Resources

You can see and explore the resources your Intelligent App installs. When the app instance has installed successfully, all the resources are available on this tab.

From Setup, select your app instance and click Resources.
The list includes CRM Analytics dashboards, components, and lenses; Einstein Studio and Einstein Discovery models; Data Cloud data model objects (DMO) and calculated insights, and CRM Analytics datasets; and Data Cloud data transforms and CRM Analytics recipes.

Each resource displays details such as name, last modified on, and last modified by.
